<!--<h4>Panel-I.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>© svasti śrīmatu strīkadaṁbēsvaradēvara Acārya mūṟu
<lb n="2" break="no"/>jāvidēvaru huligeṟe bijaiṁgeyvalli bisilahaḷi
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ya teṁkaṇa Ēṟuduradalli kudure pe<unclear>sa</unclear>ra bōdalli 
<lb n="4"/>mēdara pāṁḍya kuttikoṁḍu sivalōka
<lb n="5" break="no"/>prapitanāda <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ātana makkaḷi<unclear>ge</unclear> vuṁbaḷiṁ kaṁba hiri
<lb n="6"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="5" unit="character"/> ya 30
</p>

<!--<h4>Panel-II.</h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="7"/>Adakke Aḷi hōdavaru Avana peddaḷige Aḷihi
<lb n="8" break="no"/>davaru <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> matte Āta <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> ya
<lb n="9"/>na haḷiya hoṟe hu<unclear>ṭu</unclear>saluvudu
</p>

